Error: Error: "Cannot Start Server. The Allocated RAM Exceeds The Maximum Amount Allowed."

Solution: 1. Log into your Pterodactyl control panel and navigate to the "Schedules" section.
2. Select the "Task Manager" option.
3. Click the "Create" button to create a new task.
4. Fill out the task form with the following:
   - Task Name: Restart Server
   - Action: Send command
   - Command: stop
   - User:
